fashion_dress_34.Name: Seaside Vacation
fashion_dress_34.Description: It's time to kick back and relax! I heard that Banges is having a Graceday Celebration event...

fashion_dress_26.Name: Desert Aurora
fashion_dress_26.Description: Put away your tired body and wear a coat of rough gravel. Welcome to this land of sand.

fashion_dress_19.Name: Wasteland
fashion_dress_19.Description: Marketed as both "gorgeous and dangerous," this outfit marks a breakthrough in the designer's craft, inspired by classical design.

fashion_dress_18.Name: Forget Me Not
fashion_dress_18.Description: An outfit suitable for extremely high-temperature environments. Provides adventurers with only the most basic shelter.

fashion_dress_17.Name: Rising Gale
fashion_dress_17.Description: Exhibit a sporty style that matches your youthfulness and vitality!

fashion_dress_16.Name: Machine Era
fashion_dress_16.Description: In a world where human modification becomes increasingly commonplace, the intersection of function and fashion becomes all the more important, as well.

fashion_dress_14.Name: Sunbeam Voyager
fashion_dress_14.Description: Prioritizing functionality above all, this lightweight garment is equipped with a buckle for carrying additional items—a popular choice among those with more itinerant lifestyles.

fashion_dress_13.Name: Nightwalk
fashion_dress_13.Description: A prominent fashion designer's first foray into creating combat attire. Aside from being fashionably relevant, the torso is also equipped with ultra-thin alloy armor plating.

fashion_dress_2.Name: Scavenger Outfit
fashion_dress_2.Description: A simple and practical outfit for scavengers.

fashion_dress_20.Name: Absolute Order
fashion_dress_20.Description: A suit designed in accordance with the uniform of a governmental department before the Cataclysm. Effects a dignified and serious air.

fashion_dress_10.Name: Conqueror
fashion_dress_10.Description: A lightweight and durable adventurer's suit with plenty of pockets. The best choice for long-distance travel.

fashion_dress_3.Name: Universal Work Clothes
fashion_dress_3.Description: Warm, light, and breathable work clothes. Suitable for areas with minimal temperature change.

fashion_dress_11.Name: Last Stand
fashion_dress_11.Description: Geared towards mobility-minded adventurers, this outfit completely abandons any protective design considerations.

fashion_dress_6.Name: Visitor in the Snow
fashion_dress_6.Description: A cold-resistant combat suit with powerful heat preservation functionality. Can resist low temperatures in severely cold regions.

fashion_dress_4.Name: Wastelands Wanderer
fashion_dress_4.Description: The first combat suit with a split upper and lower design, breaking the shackles of tradition. However, the exposed torso has proved to be a polarizing aspect among critics.

fashion_dress_7.Name: Roamer
fashion_dress_7.Description: The Hykros suit made of a material that maintains a constant temperature. Can keep you warm while protecting you from the sun. A sensible choice for travelers.

fashion_dress_9.Name: Star Sand
fashion_dress_9.Description: Combat attire that boasts excellent malleability, as well as an ergonomic design that perfectly conforms to human skin.

fashion_dress_8.Name: The Mission
fashion_dress_8.Description: Combat attire that boasts excellent malleability, as well as an ergonomic design that perfectly conforms to human skin.

fashion_dress_12.Name: Desperado
fashion_dress_12.Description: A rough and wild style, designed for adventurers who like to show off their personality.

fashion_dress_15.Name: Operation: Streamer
fashion_dress_15.Description: An experiment in both fashion and technology, featuring optical cloaking materials inlaid in the cloth and decorated with suspension components.

fashion_decoration_28.Name: Goggles
fashion_decoration_28.Description: Wear them and be transformed into the talk of the town!

fashion_decoration_27.Name: Demon Doctor
fashion_decoration_27.Description: Are you my test subject for today?

fashion_decoration_5.Name: Red Heart Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_5.Description: Have you ever been blinded by love?

fashion_decoration_6.Name: Pirate Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_6.Description: Sorry, I really don't know how to draw bones.

fashion_decoration_30.Name: White Gauze Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_30.Description: Originally used as a medical eyepatch, it somehow became a popular fashion accessory. Wearing it supposedly makes you look cooler, which adds to its popularity.

fashion_decoration_32.Name: Black Eye Band
fashion_decoration_32.Description: This type of eyewear shot up in popularity after the superstar Udamu was seen wearing them and has no shortage of imitators... But can you really see that well after putting them on?
fashion_decoration_32.ActiveSource: Apex League - Star General Rank Results

fashion_decoration_33.Name: Particle Lens
fashion_decoration_33.Description: Features an ultra-high-performance microcomputer that can take photos according to your visual distance and intraocular imaging, and analyzes the composition and structure of all objects in front of you.
fashion_decoration_33.ActiveSource: Apex League - Battle Lord Rank Results

fashion_decoration_34.Name: Windchaser Hairband
fashion_decoration_34.Description: A fashionable hairband that is very popular in Banges. Sporting a simple shape as well as unique patterns and colors, this item sells out almost as soon as it hit the shelves.

fashion_decoration_35.Name: Admiral's Shades
fashion_decoration_35.Description: Originally made for seafarers, these shades suddenly became popular in Banges due to their unique shape and color, and later a symbol of high fashion.

fashion_decoration_35_bilibili.Name: ACE Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_35_bilibili.Description: Have you ever been blinded by love?

fashion_decoration_36_haoyou.Name: Swimmer's Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_36_haoyou.Description: Have you ever been blinded by love?

fashion_decoration_37_jiuyou.Name: Series 9 Eye Mask
fashion_decoration_37_jiuyou.Description: Have you ever been blinded by love?

fashion_decoration_38_oppo.Name: Progressive Professor
fashion_decoration_38_oppo.Description: Are you my test subject for today?

fashion_decoration_39_huawei.Name: White Gauze Eyepatch
fashion_decoration_39_huawei.Description: Originally used as a medical eyepatch, it somehow became a popular fashion accessory. Wearing it supposedly makes you look cooler, which adds to its popularity.

fashion_decoration_40_tap.Name: Dr. Tap
fashion_decoration_40_tap.Description: Are you my test subject for today?

fashion_decoration_65.Name: Electric Wave Mask
fashion_decoration_65.Description: Due to the influence of unknown electric waves, one can't help but put on this mask. It's time to set off in search of your own kind!

fashion_decoration_69.Name: Hanging silk
fashion_decoration_69.Description: There are always some tiny little things with no good values other than being watched.

fashion_decoration_70.Name: Amplification Goggles
fashion_decoration_70.Description: Looks familiar... Am I able to see the world in her eyes?

fashion_glider_3.Name: Orion
fashion_glider_3.Description: Tired of the Jetpack's look? It's time to add something new to your flight experience!
